root: ^You're back! I hope your little break was nice.
^Now that the shop is open, its time to start serving customers!
^Orders come out pretty fast, and our chefs *literally* toss items out as they finish!
^You'll have to catch them as they come out, using the MOUSE to guide your platter towards all those tasty morsels.
^I know you'll be able to do it. Good luck!
